11
00:06:55,714 --> 00:06:58,509
<i>May I introduce
Mr. J. Willecomb Bellows,</i>

12
00:06:58,967 --> 00:07:00,928
<i>inventor of the Bellows
Feeding Machine,</i>

13
00:07:01,303 --> 00:07:04,348
<i>a practical device which
automatically feeds your men at work.</i>

14
00:07:04,681 --> 00:07:07,518
<i>Don't stop for lunch.
Be ahead of your competitor.</i>

15
00:07:07,684 --> 00:07:09,812
<i>The Bellows feeding machine
will eliminate the lunch hour,</i>

16
00:07:10,103 --> 00:07:13,232
<i>increase your production
and decrease your overhead.</i>

17
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:16,527
<i>Allow us to point out some of the
features of this wonderful machine.</i>

18
00:07:16,902 --> 00:07:19,696
<i>Its beautiful aerodynamic
streamlined body,</i>

19
00:07:19,863 --> 00:07:24,451
<i>its smoothness of action made silent
by electroporous metal ball bearings.</i>

20
00:07:24,618 --> 00:07:27,412
<i>Let us acquaint you
with our automaton soup plate,</i>

21
00:07:27,663 --> 00:07:30,541
<i>its compressed air blower,
no breath necessary,</i>

22
00:07:30,707 --> 00:07:33,085
<i>no energy required to cool the soup.</i>

23
00:07:33,252 --> 00:07:36,338
<i>Notice the revolving plate
with the automatic food pusher.</i>

24
00:07:36,630 --> 00:07:39,383
<i>Observe our countershaft
double-knee action cornfeeder,</i>

25
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:41,093
<i>with its synchromesh transmission,</i>

26
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:44,972
<i>enabling you to shift gears
by the mere tip of the tongue.</i>

27
00:07:45,139 --> 00:07:48,100
<i>Then there is the hydrocompressed
sterilized mouth wiper.</i>

28
00:07:48,267 --> 00:07:51,937
<i>Its factors of control insure
against spots on the shirt front.</i>

29
00:07:52,104 --> 00:07:53,856
<i>These are but a few
of the delightful features</i>

30
00:07:54,022 --> 00:07:55,566
<i>of the Bellows Feeding Machine.</i>

31
00:07:55,899 --> 00:07:59,778
<i>Let us demonstrate with a worker.
Actions speak louder than words.</i>

32
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:02,072
<i>Remember,
to keep ahead of your competitor,</i>

33
00:08:02,239 --> 00:08:06,410
